Indacoin,is,a,cryptocurrency,platform,that,allows,users,to,purchase,Bitcoin,and,LiteCoin,with,a,credit,card,The,Indacoin,public,API,allows,any,developer,to,send,an,HTTP,request,to,Indacoin,to,receive,information,on,recent,orders,trades,and,current,market,prices,With,an,API,key,developers,can,schedule,orders,view,balances,view,transaction,histories,and,perform,basic,order,maintenance